snippet.title: Katamari Damacy Reroll Walkthrough Gameplay Part 1 - No Commentary (PC)
snippet.description:
Katamari Damacy Reroll Gameplay Walkthrough Part 1 No Commentary Playthrough on PC in 1080p HD (Steam Remastered Puzzle Game 2018)
►Subscribe: https://goo.gl/cjMxQC
►Playlist: https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLDKgbJ4iSaZuGZ00L1j04Hc9nkgjOldO_
►Start Another Completed Series: https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLDKgbJ4iSaZt8WGUKTPRn0bULXBLmZi1w

"The stop-at-nothing pushing prince is back and ready to REROLL! When the King of All Cosmos accidentally destroys all the stars in the sky, he orders you, his pint-sized princely son, to put the twinkle back in the heavens above. Join the King and Prince of Cosmos on their wacky adventure to restore the stars at home or on the go. The beloved roll-em-up game returns with fully updated graphics, completely recreated cutscenes and in full HD!"
